            "Unstyled mode ships no plugin CSS. Your theme styles everything through the semantic .sieve-* classes (.sieve-app, .sieve-facet, .sieve-chip, .sieve-search, \u2026). Keyboard focus and high-contrast cues are still emitted.": [
